<div style="background-color:#FFFF99"><p>Note that this data was principally compiled for internal documentation purposes and is not as <em>polished</em> as full cataloguing would accomplish.  As such, there are minor errors in spelling, punctuation etc.  None of these films are yet available to view but we are working towards this.  We would hope to be able to offer digitisation (for viewing purposes only initially) at some point, once we have dealt with the preservation issues that affect much of the collection.</p></div>